CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 20, 1954, pg. 26, reads: "New Champs - Members of Ammon Center's Junior basketball team which won the Department of Parks and Recreation basketball crown last week, defeating Ammon, 32-26, are pictured above. Shown, left to right, front row: H. Williams, R. Gloster, C. Biffens and V. White.  Back row: J. Wallace, R. Ledbetter, Charlie Betts, coach; R. Hughes and D. Bailey.  The team won 18 and dropped two during the season. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ammon Center Junior basketball team, front row from left: H. Williams, R. Gloster, C. Biffens, and V. White; back row: J. Wallace, R. Ledbetter, coach Charlie Betts, R. Hughes, and D. Bailey, posed in gymnasium
